<lb n="0445c15" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0445c1501">甲冑陀羅尼曰。</p>
<lb n="0445c16" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0445c1601" type="dharani">伊唐葛哩摩<note place="inline">二合</note>酤嚕那謨<note place="inline">引</note><note n="0445009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔窣〕－【元】</note><app n="0445009"><lem wit="【大】">窣</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】">&lac;</rdg></app>&CB00418;<note place="inline">二合</note>底莎<note place="inline">引</note>
<lb n="0445c17" ed="T"/>賀<note place="inline">引一句</note></p>
